_sText:
Hii

This is my first Camera view Plane map. Learn how to drive and shoot before you go to war =)
 
Tel me what you like and dont like and all bug to fix next version. 

[Video 1...](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7hfehYJ3Yx8 "Video1")

[Video 2 ion cannon...](http://www.youtube.com/watch?NR=1&feature=endscreen&v=QqFWVBW65cc "video")

How to play:

1. Destroy enemy ship ore plane to win
2. To drive plane press: Up/Down/Left/Right
3. Shoot press: reload button
4. Speed boost press: Left mouse
5. 20 plane total in map and 2 aircraftcarrier
6. Music battlefield

* Entdata was 120% Very high when compile normal, But no crash so far on server =)

If you want make map with this plane download the new update F22 Plane: [F22 new update...](http://www.gamebanana.com/prefabs/5679 "prefabe F22")

Have fun
